===Sprites===
==Trivia==
*In ''Rune Factory 3'', [[Raven (RF3)|Raven]] and [[Micah]] are the only known characters to have another form besides [[Pia]] since Pia is a mermaid. Although she has a monster form in ''Rune Factory 3'', Raven will not change from her human form to her monster form in ''Rune Factory 4''.
*When doing the "Mood Reversal Potion" event, if you talk to Raven while carrying the potion, she will believe that she is a "golden wooly" who was chasing monsters into the town
*Raven mentions that there is an [[Daria|elf in her town]] who resembles [[Margaret]] and [[Illuminata]].
*Her store's name is [[Sakuya]], which is named after a [[Shino|friend]]'s daughter.

